snippet.title: Rising World Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Our game Rising World will be available on Steam on 3rd of december 2014! Stay tuned!

Rising World (formerly known as "Concept") is an open-world sandbox game, featuring a randomly generated and fully destructible terrain, playable in single and multi-player.

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/324080
Homepage: https://www.rising-world.net/
Forum: https://forum.rising-world.net/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jiwgames
Twitter: https://twitter.com/JIWGames
IndieDB: http://www.indiedb.com/games/risingworld
